<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Gohankun of Tarew Marr</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-18 20:15:49</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>As always, this spell is always misinterpreted throughout sites around the web. This spell does NOT do 27HP only. There are 3-4 layers that fall (depend on level and skill), and EACH layer does 27HP a piece. If a creature resists one layer, he can still get slaughtered with the others. Few resisist every single layer of Hail.</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
